# Demo/input data for the Code Ocean capsule is not tracked in git (files are
# far too large for GitHub - see CodeOcean_Capsule/data/README.md). Upload
# data directly to Code Ocean as a Data Asset instead.
CodeOcean_Capsule/data/*.mat
CodeOcean_Capsule/results/*
!CodeOcean_Capsule/results/.gitkeep
